content.problemStatement:
Which of the following snippets correctly use comments in C?

**A.**

```c
// Display the months
printf("January February March April");
```

**B.**

```c
/* Display the months */
printf("January February March April");
```

**C.**

```c
// Single-line
/* Multi-line comment */
printf("January February March April");
```

**D.**

```c
/ Display the months /
printf("January February March April");
```

